<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='4999:5039'><span class='krp-note'>誓告/汝士</span>王曰<span class='krp-note'>誓/曰</span>古人有言曰牝雞無晨<span class='krp-note'>古人言母雞/無鳴晨之理</span>牝雞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='5039:5072'>之晨惟家之索<span class='krp-note'>母雞鳴晨則物反常/為殀家必索而盡</span>今商王受惟婦言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='5072:5113'>是用<span class='krp-note'>紂惟妲已之言是/用是牝雞而鳴晨</span>昬棄厥肆祀弗荅<span class='krp-note'>冝其昬於事/神則棄其所</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='5113:5152'><span class='krp-note'>常陳之祭祀而/其不能報本</span>昬棄厥遺王父母弟不迪<span class='krp-note'>王父母之昆/弟母弟同母</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='5152:5192'><span class='krp-note'>弟皆棄其骨肉/不案之以道</span>乃惟四方之多罪逋逃<span class='krp-note'>乃聚四方之多/罪而逋走逃亡</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='5192:5228'><span class='krp-note'>者/</span>是崇是長是信是使<span class='krp-note'>於是尊崇之推長/之親信之任使之</span>是以為大夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='5228:5254'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0035', 'WYG', '006-8b' );" name="006-8b" class="pb">[006-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
